@blog_community_api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5158/api

### Register User
POST {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser1",
    "email": "test1@example.com",
    "password": "P@ssword!"
}

### Login testuser1
POST {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "testuser1",
  "password": "P@ssword!"
}

### Login testuser2
POST {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
