### Get By User ID
GET {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/users/{{userId1}}
##Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Get By Username
GET {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/users/{{username1}}
Accept: application/json

### Update User
PUT {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/users/{{userId1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updatedUser",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

### Delete User
DELETE {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/users/{{userId1}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### Create Category as testuser1
POST {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Skiing"
}

### List Categories
GET {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/Categories

### Create Blog post as testuser1
POST {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/BlogPosts
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": "3a6b0e59-4bf8-4fef-94b0-80c0b913f1b4",
  "title": "My First Post About Skiing",
  "content": "This is the content"
}

### List Blog posts
GET {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/blogposts

### Filter Blog posts by title
GET {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/blogposts?title=skiing

### Filter Blog posts by category
GET {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/BlogPosts?categoryId=3a6b0e59-4bf8-4fef-94b0-80c0b913f1b4

### Get Blog post by ID
GET {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/blogposts/a59b9d2e-438b-47f2-ab88-3e489d3e2ccc

### Update Blog post
PUT {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/blogposts/d6dcf7de-7b97-4950-8b9c-1c508cfe6e8c
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": "cda2b101-f8bb-4859-9932-50a41e989ce2",
  "title": "My First Post About Fishing",
  "content": "Fishing stuff"
}

### Delete Blog post
DELETE {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/blogposts/98d4e0bc-1ef4-4342-87dd-a99c76b03a72 
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### testuser2 comment on testuser1's post
