Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "comment on skiing post"
}

### Get comments for post
GET {{blog_community_api_HostAddress}}/blogposts/d6dcf7de-7b97-4950-8b9c-1c508cfe6e8c/comments

